":"The LORD executeth righteousness and judgment for all that are oppressed.","year":-1034},{"id":"recpIWS5BQzZNIpF7","ref":"Ps.103.7","text":"He made known his ways unto Moses, his acts unto the children of Israel.","year":-1034},{"id":"recEtlx5sxadxLcxu","ref":"Ps.103.8","text":"The LORD is merciful and gracious, slow to anger, and plenteous in mercy.","year":-1034}]}
